  "title": "fix: switch back to divs in refinementList, rendering glitch",
  "body": "To be more precise: `<ul>` has a default margin of 10px bottom in bootstrap. It's not an issue if you precisely follow the bootstrap DOM format but otherwise it does not works.\n\nSo `<div>` being unstyled by default will in the end by easier to use for most websites.\n\nExample:\n\n![2015-09-09-100326_293x158_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/9756387/0dfc1b7c-56da-11e5-841a-4f59eb16a366.png)\n",
